name: The Goblin's Prose: A Poetry Collection
description:
A collection of thirteen poems I minted over the course of 2021 that I decided to burn and allocate to this single PDF. Much love to my s/o @fluidnft for supporting me and doing these illustrations.



Poems included are as follows

Page 2: Nilbog, Child of Fright
Page 3: 2006 MacBook... Bluetooth Compatible?
Page 4: Cute Anime Girl
Page 5: Dogfight in Exosphere
Page 6: Holistic Cancer
Page 7: Invisible Hologram of Dr. Dre
Page 8: Kindle to a Slaughter 
Page 9: Ivy Intertwined, My Green Thumb
Page 10: Medicinally Medieval
Page 11: Roiling Blunder
Page 12: Vindicator, the Handyman
Page 13: Slit Artery, Severed Highway
Page 14: Socialist Turning Point; USA
